TNFRSF17

Description

Tumor necrosis factor receptor superfamily member 17 (TNFRSF17). Receptor for TNFSF13B/BLyS/BAFF and TNFSF13/APRIL. Promotes B-cell survival and plays a role in the regulation of humoral immunity. Activates NF-kappa-B and JNK.


Clinical trials

NCT03302403 - Hepatocellular Carcinoma, Pancreatic Cancer
